doc.after: Dubai International Airport was conceptualised to function as Dubai s primary airport and the region s busiest for the foreseeable future without the need for relocation or the building of another airport when passenger figures increased The area was chosen near to Dubai to attract passengers from the city of Dubai rather than travel to the busier Sharjah International Airport The planned location originally was Jebel Ali 70
